narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Private lessons are a great way to keep up your technique and learn new things with a different teacher!
I would definitely recommend voice lessons to another student.
This is a good class to take, especially if you are involved in any of Yale's music groups.

If your in any sort of performance group, this class, regardless of the style will improve your sound and performance abilities. Definitely take the class if you have the time and prerequisites. It's super chill.
